t\n!\nlog file /tmp/logging\n\n!\nip forwarding\nvrf mgmt\n exit-vrf\n!\nfrr defaults datacenter\n!\ninterface lo\n no shutdown\n ip address 10.0.0.1/32\n!\ninterface eth1\n no shutdown\n description dut -> [r2,rs] [external]\n ip address 172.16.0.1/24\n!\ninterface eth2\n no shutdown\n description dut -> r3 [external]\n ip address 10.1.0.1/30\n!\ndo write\nCONFIG\nvtysh -f /tmp/config\n!\nexit 0\n"
